commitResults.messageBody:
Implements a basic version of Level-4 increments. Task of its
respective type will be added by scanning the first word of the user
input.

First word is case-insensitive and ignores any whitespaces that may
have been accidentally added in front.

Let's add addTask, splitDescriptionFromTiming, and removeFirstWord
methods to achieve the implementation of this project increment.
* Display help message when invalid input is detected
